CB-V61
Features	Specs	Support
Versatile Carrying Bag for Portable 61-Note Keyboards

The CB-V61 bag is a versatile carrying solution for portable 61-note keyboards like GO:KEYS 3, GO:KEYS 5, JUNO-D6, and other Roland models. Whether using the comfortable carrying handles or padded backpack straps, traveling to music sessions is easy with this quality bag.

Standard Features
Fits many 61-note Roland keyboards: GO:KEYS 3, GO:KEYS 5, FANTOM-06, JUNO-D6, E-X10, XPS-60, and more
Durable polyester exterior
Three removable internal cushions and a securing strap to accommodate different keyboard models
Hideaway backpack straps
Versatile front pocket for accessories and the optional music rest for GO:KEYS models (MRGKS3/5)
Custom Roland zipper pulls
Includes three key chains with Roland, JUNO, and GO:KEYS logos
Inside dimensions: 1030 x 325 x 90 mm
Customizable Protection

The CB-V61 protects your keyboard at home and on the move. It features a durable polyester exterior, an adjustable internal securing strap, and three removable cushions that allow you to customize the fit for your instrument’s dimensions.

Large Storage Pocket

With the CB-V61's large front pocket, you have a convenient home for stowing cables, AC cords, and other essential accessories. It’s also the perfect size to carry the optional music rest for the Roland GO:KEYS 3 and GO:KEYS 5 models.

Three Key Chains

Carry your keys in style and show off your favorite keyboard brands with three included key chains that feature Roland, JUNO, and GO:KEYS logos.
